- [Usage](#usage)
- [Project Structure](#project-structure)
- [Model Evaluation](#model-evaluation)
- [License](#license)

---

## 📊 Project Overview

The goal of this project is to build a regression model that can accurately estimate the price of a car using historical data. This can be used by customers and dealers to better understand car value and make informed decisions.

---

## 🧰 Tech Stack

- Python 🐍
- Pandas & NumPy (data handling)
- Matplotlib & Seaborn (data visualization)
- Scikit-learn (machine learning)

---

